Turn around and go to the wall, then turn right to go to the black end table.
Put the watch on the black end table.
Turn around and go forward, then turn left to go to the coffee table.
Pick up the watch from the coffee table.
Turn around and go to the wall, then turn right to go to the black end table.
Put the watch on the black end table.

Turn left, turn left, walk straight, turn right, walk straight to the table with the black lamp.
Put the watch on the table.
Turn right, turn right, walk straight, turn left to the small black table
Pick up the watch on the table.
Turn left, turn left, walk straight, turn right, walk straight to the table with the black lamp.
Put the watch on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the black coffee table and take a small step to your right.
Pick up the watch that's in front of you on the coffee table.

Put the watch on the end table.
Turn around and walk to the coffee table that's on your left.
Pick up the watch that's in front of you on the coffee table..
Walk back to where you put the first watch.
